title: Doctor In the House, 1969-70,  British TV comedy, complete
description:
A complete set of episodes from both Seasons, originally aired in 1969-1970. A light hearted and somewhat truthful look at what it was like being a medical student in late 1960s Britain, peppered with traditional British values of sexism, elitism and occasional racism. 
The resolution is only 480, because that is what TV's did back then, when a 23-inch set was considered large and luxurious
